# macOS
.DS_Store

# Rust build artifacts
/target/

# Compiled driver WASMs and packaged artifacts (build outputs — uploaded to GitHub Releases)
**/*.wasm
**/*.mur.zip

# Backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# Runtime output directories produced by mur run / test invocations
**/checkpoints/
**/workdir/
.nexus/

# murmur-tool-editor on-disk read cache — created in the CWD at dispatch time and by the
# crate's host-target cache unit tests; a runtime artifact, never committed. The broader
# **/ glob subsumes the narrower tools/murmur-tool-editor/-scoped rule this replaces.
**/.murmur-tool-editor-cache/

# murmur-tool-code-graph on-disk graph db + slice payloads — created under a target
# repo's .murmur/ at index/slice time; a runtime artifact, never committed.
**/.murmur/
